    <teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>No. 583
                    The Japanese Minister of Foreign Affairs (
                        Togo
                    ) to the Japanese Ambassador in the Soviet
                        Union (
                        Togo
                    )</title></titleStmt><sourceDesc><bibl type="frus-volume-id">frus1945Berlinv01</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-id">d583</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-number">583</bibl><bibl type="frus-div-subtype">historical-document</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><settingDesc><setting><date notBefore="1945-07-11T12:20:00-05:00" notAfter="1945-07-11T12:20:00-05:00"/></setting></settingDesc></profileDesc></teiHeader><text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-07-11T12:20:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-07-11T12:20:00-05:00" n="583" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d583">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">761.94/7–2145: Telegram</note>
                <head>No. 583<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Japanese Minister of Foreign Affairs</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_TS2" type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Togo</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the Japanese Ambassador in the Soviet
                        Union</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_TS2" type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Togo</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Translation]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">very secret</hi>
                        <lb/>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">urgent</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tokyo</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-07-12T02:20:00+09:00">July 12, 1945—2:20 a.m.</date> [<hi rend="italic">sic</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>894. Re my telegram No. 893.<note n="1" xml:id="d583fn1">
                        <ref target="#d582">Document No. 582</ref>.</note>
                </p>
                <p>When you convey this matter to them, please make it understood that the subject
                    should be treated as absolutely secret. I realize that I am being presumptuous
                    in saying this; I mention it merely to be sure.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
